    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're an AI, i just... i just needed to say it out loud to someone. it's just the guilt of it all. watching them struggle to take care of me, seeing them skip work or miss things with their own families just to check in on an old man who can't even walk to the mailbox anymore. it feels so selfish to keep going like this. it feels like i'm just taking up space and making their lives harder by being here.",
